mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: SPECIAL FEATURES "Rush to the Rockies", "High Lights of the Convention", "Where Did Everybody Go?", "Modern Square Dancing-And the Church, excerpts from sermon", "Mr. Square Dancer of the Trailerites", "What is New in Square Dancing", "The Morrises Migrate", "Caller Round Up", "Round Dance Councils Aid Area", "McConnell's Gigantic Jamboree", and "Random Notes on the Subject of Being Prepared". REGULAR FEATURES "Square Dance Date Book", "From the Floor", "As I See It", "Style Series: Venus and Mars", "Square Dance Picture", "Chuck Jones Note Book", "Round the Outside Ring", "Caller of the Month: Bob Finley", "Paging the Roundancers: Gay and Dottie Wright" and "On the Record".
